Include the Altitude marketing logo and create a sidebar with sections for an Overview page with 4 cards for Color system tokens, Typescale tokens, components, and theme previewer that each link to their respective pages, and the rest of the info currently organized in the horizontal button-style navigation. Do not edit the existing files; create a new react/nextjs app that I can run locally to preview updates before pushing the code live. You can use the Tailwind color system but make sure to ONLY USE the css variables outlined in the JSON and CSS files. You MUST follow the same primitives and semantic names and 8px grid system.

+ export default function PreviewPage() {
+   const [brandColor, setBrandColor] = useState('#2AAFB8');
+   const [secondaryColor, setSecondaryColor] = useState('#444B8C');
+   const [typeScale, setTypeScale] = useState&lt;'ms' | 'mt'&gt;('mt');
+   const [spacingMultiplier, setSpacingMultiplier] = useState(1);
+   const [selectedPreset, setSelectedPreset] = useState('Altitude (Default)');
+   
+   const previewRef = useRef&lt;HTMLDivElement&gt;(null);
+ 
+   useEffect(() =&gt; {
+     if (!previewRef.current) return;
+     const style = previewRef.current.style;
+ 
+     // Update colors
+     style.setProperty('--color-brand', brandColor);
+     style.setProperty('--color-brand-hover', brandColor);
+     style.setProperty('--color-secondary', secondaryColor);
+     style.setProperty('--color-secondary-hover', secondaryColor);
+     style.setProperty('--button-bg', brandColor);
+     style.setProperty('--button-bg-hover', brandColor);
+ 
+     // Update typography scale
+     const scale = typeScale === 'ms' ? '--ms' : '--mt';
+     style.setProperty('--font-size-caption', &#96;var(--font-size-2xs${scale})&#96;);
+     style.setProperty('--font-size-label', &#96;var(--font-size-xs${scale})&#96;);
+     style.setProperty('--font-size-body-small', &#96;var(--font-size-sm${scale})&#96;);
+     style.setProperty('--font-size-body', &#96;var(--font-size-md${scale})&#96;);
+     style.setProperty('--font-size-lead', &#96;var(--font-size-lg${scale})&#96;);
+     style.setProperty('--font-size-h6', &#96;var(--font-size-xl${scale})&#96;);
+     style.setProperty('--font-size-h5', &#96;var(--font-size-2xl${scale})&#96;);
+     style.setProperty('--font-size-h4', &#96;var(--font-size-3xl${scale})&#96;);
+     style.setProperty('--font-size-h3', &#96;var(--font-size-4xl${scale})&#96;);
+     style.setProperty('--font-size-h2', &#96;var(--font-size-5xl${scale})&#96;);
+     style.setProperty('--font-size-h1', &#96;var(--font-size-6xl${scale})&#96;);
+ 
+     // Update spacing (using CSS calc with multiplier)
+     const baseSpacings = [2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 8, 10, 12, 16];
+     baseSpacings.forEach(s =&gt; {
+       const baseValue = s * 0.25; // rem
+       style.setProperty(&#96;--spacing-${s}&#96;, &#96;${baseValue * spacingMultiplier}rem&#96;);
+     });
+ 
+   }, [brandColor, secondaryColor, typeScale, spacingMultiplier]);
+ 
+   const applyPreset = (preset: ColorPreset) =&gt; {
+     setBrandColor(preset.brand);
+     setSecondaryColor(preset.secondary);
+     setSelectedPreset(preset.name);
+   };
+ 
+   const resetDefaults = () =&gt; {
+     setBrandColor('#2AAFB8');
+     setSecondaryColor('#444B8C');
+     setTypeScale('mt');
+     setSpacingMultiplier(1);
+     setSelectedPreset('Altitude (Default)');
+   };

+       {/* Header */}
+       &lt;div style={{ marginBottom: 'var(--spacing-8)' }}&gt;
+         &lt;h1
